--- 'pbdDMAC' Installation:
   Default Installation:

     C:/> set_mpisrc
     C:/> tar zxvf pbdDMAC_0.1-0.tar.gz
     C:/> R CMD INSTALL --build pbdDMAC
     C:/> R CMD INSTALL pbdDMAC_0.1-0.zip


--- Testing:
   Suppose all environments are set correctly, I can run test examples by

   -- 64-bits
     C:/> set_mpisrc 64
     C:/> mpiexec -np 2 Rscript.exe -e "demo(simple,'pbdDMAC',ask=F,echo=F)"
   -- 32-bits
     C:/> set_mpisrc 32
     C:/> mpiexec -np 2 Rscript.exe -e "demo(simple,'pbdDMAC',ask=F,echo=F)"
